properties.areaDesc: Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to Slaughter Beach DE
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 1 at 4:14AM EST until February 1 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than one mile.

* WHERE...Delaware Bay waters north of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM EST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM EST THIS MORNING
